peaksea color scheme: http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=760

use git submodules for plugins

app-vim/nerdcommenter: https://github.com/scrooloose/nerdcommenter
or, app-vim/tcomment: https://github.com/tomtom/tcomment_vim
app-vim/taglist
app-vim/tagbar
app-vim/syntastic (instead of .vim/bundle/ ?? no, git clone is better)
app-vim/supertab
app-vim/repeat: https://github.com/tpope/vim-repeat/  + the other tpope plugins listed
app-vim/recover: https://github.com/chrisbra/Recover.vim (show diff when recovering)
app-vim/python-mode ?
app-vim/fugitive
app-vim/easytags: http://peterodding.com/code/vim/easytags/
app-vim/closetag ? (XML/HTML closing tags)
app-vim/cctree: http://sites.google.com/site/vimcctree/ (Hari)
app-vim/ansiesc: http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=302 (conceal Esc chars)
app-vim/airline: https://github.com/bling/vim-airline/ (status bar)

